# 🤖 Gemini API Key Configuration
# 
# To enable AI summaries in the reports and dashboard:
# 1. Copy or rename this file to '.env' in the project root
# 2. Get your Gemini API key from https://aistudio.google.com/api-keys
# 3. Paste the key below (e.g. GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy...)
# 
# NOTE: The application will function perfectly even without this key configured.
# If the key is not set, AI features will be gracefully skipped.
#
GEMINI_API_KEY=
